---
title: "Theming: Customising Selections"
---

Control how selected rows and cells appear.

## Row Selections

When [row selection](./row-selection/) is enabled, you can set the color of selected rows using the `selectedRowBackgroundColor` parameter. If your grid uses alternating row colours we recommend setting this to a semi-transparent colour so that the alternating row colours are visible below it.

```js
const myTheme = themeQuartz.withParams({
    /* bright green, 10% opacity */
    selectedRowBackgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1)',
});
```

